The paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques to obtain a color illumination invariant and shadow-free image from a single outdoor image. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of Lab color space, which falls under the category of graphics (cs.GR). Additionally, the paper involves the use of statistical learning, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves the use of linear equations and orthogonal decomposition, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG).
